&lt;li&gt;Assisting with special projects, including coordinating executive visits while in Japan, office events planning and execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing and ordering office supplies, including stationery, drinks, and snacks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handling incoming and outgoing mail and packages, including sorting and shipping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating with the building management company to maintain a clean and hygienic office space by ensuring it is kept tidy and organized.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide support for new hires such as ordering business cards, security cards, other necessary setup, and implementation of Office onboarding.&lt;/li&gt;
