&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent communication skills; able to explain complex concepts clearly and confidently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
