&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Own the end-to-end partner strategy for Cloudflare’s Developer Platform—spanning channel partners (SIs/MSPs/service providers) and technology alliances (integrations, co-builds). Your mandate: prioritize the right partners, ship joint solutions, and align GTM so developers can adopt and scale faster—with measurable, partner-sourced and influenced revenue. You’ll set the strategy centrally and execute through the regional partner teams. (Cloudflare programs include technology partnerships aligned to developer services and other solution areas; partner network spans technology, global SIs, and service providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set the ecosystem strategy: Map, segment, and prioritize partners (channel + tech) that matter for developer workloads; publish a focused “top-X” plan per region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build technology alliances: Land integrations and reference architectures that improve customer outcomes on Workers/Workers AI, R2/D1/KV, Queues, Stream, and real-time primitives; define validation and co-support paths. (Cloudflare’s tech partnerships drive integrations and joint GTM aligned to Developer Services.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-sell / co-market plays: Create repeatable partner plays (ICP, offer, proof, pricing posture), enable regional partner managers, and measure attach/impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Channel acceleration: With SIs/MSPs/service providers, package implementation offers and services SKUs; raise partner capability and profitability with clear enablement and “give/get.”&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Program alignment: Coordinate listings and offers where relevant; align with central partner programs for readiness and incentives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate through regions: Run a global partner operating rhythm (monthly reviews, quarterly plans) through regional leaders; unblock deals and integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the scorecard: Partner-sourced and influenced pipeline/bookings, integration launches and adoption, partner attach on priority workloads, enablement completion, and partner NPS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builder, not just broker: 10+ years across channel + developer/alliances; you’ve shipped integrations and built co-sell machines with SIs/MSPs/tech partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developer-fluent: Comfortable with workloads, APIs/SDKs, reference architectures, and how developers evaluate platforms; you translate technical value to commercial outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operator with range: You write crisp plans, run a global cadence, and drive matrixed execution with Sales, Product, PMM, Finance, and Legal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Metrics-driven: You size opportunities, forecast partner impact, and hold partners (and us) to results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Global &amp;amp; pragmatic: Experience working across Americas/EMEA/APAC through regional partner teams; clear communicator, excellent collaborator.&lt;/li&gt;
