&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coaching Ability:&lt;/strong&gt; Demonstrated ability to provide constructive feedback and executive coaching to internal speakers and stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
