&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Literacy:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience using data and analytics tools to measure program ROI and sentiment, with the ability to translate insights into strategic action.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
