&lt;li&gt;Experience working with async software patterns like queues, pub-sub, and event buses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience debugging, optimizing and identifying failure modes in&amp;nbsp;a large-scale Linux-based distributed system.&lt;/li&gt;
