&lt;li data-start=&quot;3231&quot; data-end=&quot;3274&quot;&gt;DMP partner activation and productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3275&quot; data-end=&quot;3328&quot;&gt;Pipeline contribution aligned to regional targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
