&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for a leader who enjoys a mix of hunting, structured qualification, and consultative high velocity selling. You will work closely with Digital Solutions Engineers, Customer Success, and regional leadership to sharpen your team’s commercial skills and make a visible impact on Cloudflare’s growth in the region.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;What you will do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Lead and manage a regional team of ISRs to meet or exceed monthly and quarterly revenue targets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Coach the team on hunting, structured qualification and consultative selling to drive new business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Support ISRs in managing multiple deals at different stages, ensuring high-velocity execution from first contact to close.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Use Salesforce and data-driven insights to manage the regional pipeline and provide accurate forecasting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with Recruiting, Marketing to hire top sales talent and optimize lead flow across our APAC hubs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
