&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Proven experience managing a team of quota-carrying sales representatives, preferably in the APAC region.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of high-velocity sales cycles within the small and midsize market. (Sub 300 employees)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Demonstrated record of meeting or exceeding sales targets as both a leader and an individual contributor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Strong discovery and qualification skills with the ability to coach others on framework execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to manage and lead distributed teams across multiple time zones and cultures (specifically India, Greater China, Korea, and ANZ).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent communication and negotiation skills with a proactive approach to outbound prospecting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborative mindset and comfort working with both technical and non-technical teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eligibility to work in Singapore/Australia&lt;/p&gt;
