&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Resident Consultant at Cloudflare, you will serve as a dedicated, on-site strategic advisor for one of our high-growth enterprise accounts in Minneapolis. You will act as the primary technical bridge between the customer’s operational needs and Cloudflare’s expansive security suite, ensuring their migration from legacy systems is seamless and high-performing. We are looking for a proactive expert who thrives on building deep technical relationships, optimizing complex configurations, and championing our mission to help build a better internet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as a Trusted Advisor:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the day-to-day technical lead and Cloudflare subject matter expert, providing proactive guidance on operational best practices and industry security standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimize Application Services:&lt;/strong&gt; Take full ownership of tuning, configuration, and policy creation for Application Services to ensure maximum performance and security posture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Network Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee the ongoing health of Network Services, including Magic Transit and DDoS protection, ensuring &quot;set and forget&quot; stability while remaining ready for rapid incident response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive Migration Excellence:&lt;/strong&gt; Leverage your deep understanding of Akamai architectures to translate legacy workflows into modern, efficient Cloudflare configurations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Roadmap Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate closely with the customer to prepare their environment for future expansions into our Developer Platform (Workers) and Zero Trust architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Documentation:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain comprehensive documentation of the customer’s unique environment, policy changes, and operational procedures to ensure long-term continuity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
