&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloudflare Certifications:&lt;/strong&gt; Valid Cloudflare ASPS or ASPE certifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Modern Web Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience with Serverless computing or Edge functions (Cloudflare Workers/WebAssembly).&lt;/li&gt;
